chapters.title: Chapter 14:  Wet Things
chapters.info: Careane Fransi, p. 330—Aes Sedai of the Green Ajah. She has shoulders and arms as big as most men. She grew up in Arad Doman, and has worn the shawl for over fifty years now. She is among the sisters that are now sworn to obey Rand. Either she or Sareitha had to have been the murderess of Adeleas, and thus Black Ajah; all other suspects have been eliminated.
